abstract: "A reproducible segmented-virus analysis workflow for CCHFV Pakistan 2022 data, including synthetic demo inputs, metagenomic read QC, de novo contig discovery, BLAST-based segment classification, targeted segment consensus generation, phylogeny, and reassortment review."
